{"tid":1979574,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過因為人哋分手而好傷心","createTime":"2020-04-19T13:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T04:12:41.000Z","uid":42128,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d452d8b9f54d52bf092a01b3defef5d02dd98b39","tid":1979574,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:41:41.000Z","msg":"話說有個我好支持嘅音樂人最近同佢個一齊咗11年嘅女朋友(圈外人)分咗手,<br />\n我知道之後成個人hang哂機,<br />\n完全接受唔到<br />\n<br />\n佢哋由大學就一齊 經歷人生高低起跌,<br />\nLongD過長時間又同居埋都安然無恙.<br />\n自稱老夫老妻嘅佢哋平時都幾低調,<br />\n我都係憑啲蛛絲馬跡先知佢哋咁sweet,<br />\n而且個個都以為佢哋結婚只係遲早嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗對方, 我覺得任何人都配唔上咁優秀嘅佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男方喺出道時已經公開有女朋友(以前好少公司肯俾artist咁做),<br />\nFans留言話要做佢老婆嗰陣佢又會好認真拒絕,<br />\n平時同異性都好避忌,<br />\n目的就係唔想女朋友唔開心.<br />\n而女仔喺男方幾次需要去外地做嘢超過一年時都靜靜守候,<br />\n近幾年男方經歷人生重大打擊,<br />\n個女仔依然好支持佢鼓勵佢,<br />\n但就喺近半年啲事都有轉機嘅時候就散咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從知道分手嘅消息之後我番工都冇乜心機,<br />\n試過喺街度係咁喊係咁喊 好彩有個口罩擋吓,<br />\n一諗起佢哋就好傷心,<br />\n我一直仰賴嘅 支持住我心靈嘅嘢毫無預兆就崩塌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(sor我形容得好垃圾),<br />\n唔知係我太幸運定係依件事對我嘅打擊真係大,<br />\n好似我成世人最難過就係依件事咁.<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家應該都覺得我諗嘢好唔成熟,<br />\n甚至有啲睇唔起我,<br />\n但我都唔知點解唔關我事嘅嘢我會咁上心咁投入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗諗吓 可能我隔一排睇番依個post都會好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e67f4ce6c913e011da4d5fe945a65e691902c94","tid":1979574,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"出完post好似舒服咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2166508f2cc319b774e44ab6b1c5b77fb3a61e39","tid":1979574,"uid":233593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"Too long didn&rsquo;t read<br />\nThx for sharing"},{"pid":"85fcf714306b0187cd74aa6a9f10c01817b60333","tid":1979574,"uid":60733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:16:45.000Z","msg":"明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca381f53053a3b705c518dd03746348bce972634","tid":1979574,"uid":42128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85fcf714306b0187cd74aa6a9f10c01817b60333","tid":1979574,"uid":60733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:16:45.000Z","msg":"明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係我唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41045e9dd0b69500bdce5f34eff6f14516c0d5c4","tid":1979574,"uid":165497,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"之前聽到壞咗嘅人個單我都呆咗，<br />\n覺得原來我曾經咁羨慕嘅人都會分手"},{"pid":"1cef11ff3326d8de07966d968533106e3c896823","tid":1979574,"uid":112000,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T17:49:06.000Z","msg":"每次一知道<br />\n拍咗拖好耐或者一直都好 sweet 嘅情侶分手<br />\n就會好 sad 覺得好可惜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99017f4399b619b201f34e63742a669f8834282","tid":1979574,"uid":190197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T19:50:58.000Z","msg":"好似聽到万刀甲同Stephy 分手咁"},{"pid":"c7066a8c81ec847301004a65f0d539add7d141a0","tid":1979574,"uid":153615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T21:26:14.000Z","msg":"想知係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439023f7fed80562aaeab4c72e967e3033be177b","tid":1979574,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T21:29:01.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n人地散左，咁我就有機會乘虛而入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a77b012a16a02e6ed1c3e8f0c3a32db0865b18","tid":1979574,"uid":92334,"li